sentence: 'Israel  will  stand  together,'  says  Netanyahu  after  eight  soldiers  killed.

article_title: 'Israel will stand together,' says Netanyahu after eight soldiers killed.
sentence: Israeli  Prime  Minister  Benjamin  Netanyahu  says  the  country  will  "stand  together"  as  he  sends  condolences  to  the  families  of  the  eight  Israeli  soldiers  killed  in  Lebanon  today.
